   <lb/>continentur a<choice><orig><g ref="#nn">n̄</g></orig><reg>nn</reg></choice>otationes me<choice><orig><g ref="#ae">æ</g></orig><reg>ae</reg></choice> in <abbr>Ill.</abbr> <abbr>D.</abbr> Comitis <rs key="pers_DE-588-109091766X" type="person">Riccati</rs> <rs type="biblio" key="biblio_6MW47K34">Schediasma</rs><note/>
<lb/><choice><orig><g ref="#agrav">à</g></orig><reg>a</reg></choice> Te su<choice><orig><g ref="#mm">m̄</g></orig><reg>mm</reg></choice>a diligentia in Italicam linguam vers<choice><orig><g ref="#ae">æ</g></orig><reg>ae</reg></choice>. Maxim<choice><orig><g ref="#ae">æ</g></orig><reg>ae</reg></choice> Tibi <choice><orig><g ref="#agrav">à</g></orig><reg>a</reg></choice> me
         <lb/>debentur grati<choice><orig><g ref="#ae">æ</g></orig><reg>ae</reg></choice>, quod molestum hunc laborem inter tot negotia
         <lb/>in Te suscipere dignatus fueris; <subst><del>g</del><add>G</add></subst>ratus hinc agnosco Tuam erga nos
         <lb/>me cumprimis benevolentiam et favorem<unclear>,</unclear> hoc Tuo favore fretus
         <lb/>audeo et hunc Tibi imponere laborem ut nisi molestum fuerit
         <lb/>et si co<choice><orig><g ref="#mm">m̄</g></orig><reg>mm</reg></choice>ode fieri possit sequentes errores Typographicos, qui quidem
