<lb/>gratias ago<choice><orig>:|</orig><reg>)</reg></choice> pauci sunt, corrigendos dare velis. <abbr>Pag.</abbr> 320<choice><orig><choice><orig><g ref="#ndot">.</g></orig><reg></reg></choice></orig><reg>,</reg></choice> <choice><abbr>l.</abbr><expan>linea</expan></choice> 10<choice><orig><choice><orig><g ref="#ndot">.</g></orig><reg></reg></choice></orig><reg>,</reg></choice>
