         <lb/><add>quam </add>fovet<del> quod</del> <rs key="pers_DE-588-118509969" type="person">Patruus</rs> meus fusius explicat supponitque quod glan<pc type="hyphenation">-</pc><lb break="no"/>dul<choice><orig><g ref="#ae">æ</g></orig><reg>ae</reg></choice> in ipsa prima formatione liquore suo particulari jam imbu<pc type="hyphenation">-</pc><lb break="no"/>t<choice><orig><g ref="#ae">æ</g></orig><reg>ae</reg></choice> fuerint <choice><orig><g ref="#agrav">à</g></orig><reg>a</reg></choice> Sapientissimo nostro Creatore eodem <subst><del>tempore</del><add>modo</add></subst> quo
         <lb/>reliqu<subst><del>orum</del><add><unclear>as</unclear></add></subst> <del>nostri membrorum</del> nostr<subst><del>a</del><add>i</add></subst><del> sunt</del> corporis partes pri<pc type="hyphenation">-</pc><lb break="no"/>mum format<choice><orig><g ref="#ae">æ</g></orig><reg>ae</reg></choice> fuerunt. Quod officia Tua pro <rs type="organisation">Cathedra Mathe<pc type="hyphenation">-</pc><lb break="no"/>matica <rs key="place_GEO-3171728" type="place">Patavina</rs></rs> mihi<metamark/> <add><choice><orig>|:</orig><reg>(</reg></choice>siquidem <rs key="pers_DE-588-118509969" type="person">Patruus</rs> <add>ob recusatum ipsi petitum salarium</add> hic manere constituit<choice><orig>:|</orig><reg>)</reg></choice></add> impetranda apud <abbr>Ill.</abbr> et <abbr>Excell.</abbr> Tuos
